NAME         SIZE  ALLOC   FREE   FRAG  EXPANDSZ    CAP  DEDUP  HEALTH  ALTROOT
data        23.9G  14.6G  9.30G    48%         -    61%  1.00x  ONLINE  -
  raidz1    23.9G  14.6G  9.30G    48%         -
    sda         -      -      -      -         -
    sdb         -      -      -      -       10G
    sdc         -      -      -      -         -
.Ed
