.Nm zpool status/iostat
with the
.Fl c
option. This is a colon-separated list of directories and overrides the default
.Pa ~/.zpool.d
and
.Pa /etc/zfs/zpool.d
search paths.
.El
.Bl -tag -width "ZPOOL_SCRIPTS_ENABLED"
